    • onActionDisplayModifyPartOutsourced

      public void onActionDisplayModifyPartOutsourced(javafx.event.ActionEvent event) throws IOException
      Changes to Outsourced scene. Uses a radio button to change the scene to the Outsourced Modify Part form. It also changes an In-House object to an Outsourced object.
      Parameters:
      event - takes a button click ActionEvent. RUNTIME ERROR. The first time I ran this method I did not set up the changeInhouseMainPart method and I got an error because of the switch from Machine ID to Company Name. So I created and implemented changeInHouseMainPart to solve the error.
      Throws:
      IOException
